div.font: Prompts vs wordlist
Acceptance Criteria
- As the host, before the game starts, I can choose to use prompts instead of words.
- When I select prompts in settings, all players receive a prompt (not a word) during the share-word phase, regardless of role.

div.font: ghost/goddess of justice
Acceptance Criteria
- I might be assigned the Goddess of Justice or Ghost role, each with unique abilities.
- If I am the first eliminated, I become the Ghost and can still participate.
- As Goddess of Justice, my vote breaks ties during voting.
- The game clearly explains these roles and abilities.
